Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.25,0:00:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Friendship, love, and mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are able to give it all we've got because we have those promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Princess and Queen are two mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the keys are on Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child, but the intelligence of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To find the person who's targeting Fujieda Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Uncle will be paid ten million.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said it would be a simple case, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without solving the case he spent some of the money on a celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now he's in debt by 8 million. After being seriously shocked, he's sleeping at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.45,0:02:04.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of Uncle, Ran's mom went to meet the client.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, she encountered my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fujieda Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was murdered in a locked room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Isn't this Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,AndYukiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are the two of you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came here as a representative for the job that my husband accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The client wanted my husband to find out who wanted to kill the master of this house, Fujieda Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:03:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did he say that the one after his life is in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because under the pillow in Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Watch your back."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, "Take it easy." Both on memo paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one bullet was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one who could do that is someone within the household.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time of the crime was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! I think it was about 8 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time, everyone was watching what was happening in the surveillance room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, suddenly, Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} stood up with his hands raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was hit and collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We rushed there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We heard two gunshots coming from the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We broke down the door and when we went in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The gun is a Compact Colt 45.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three cartridge cases were dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They match the three bullet wounds on the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the criminal shot the victim from outside the window, and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So in other words, it could have been a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A towel with a burn trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably used to avoid getting the gunpowder on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could also be used for silencing the sound of the shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, go and check the gun's firing trajectory for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, check around to see if anyone saw a suspicious character around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:43.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would like you to check and see if the bullet hidden under the pillow is the same with the one that was used to shoot the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright. Inspector, bring the inspection team into the living room with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After checking everyone for gunpowder traces, take their statements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Eri's desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, there's a 10 million yen bet on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! To-Toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's leaking out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,TOILET!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So one by one, please tell the inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the 3 minutes from when Mikio was shot in the audio room until we found his corpse,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you and what were you doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to my room to get the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I went to the audio room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to my own room to call the police and an ambulance,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that I stayed locked up in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!? Even though you knew that your husband was shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the person with the gun could've still been wandering around the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That could be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I saw Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} get shot along with the butler and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I'm being suspected shouldn't I have left the room before he was shot just like Shigeru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:05.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I wanted to go back to my room to write my manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to the audio room with Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because we heard a gunshot twice in front of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, when you went into the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hear any suspicious sounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The volume of the classical music was very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Inspector{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, is it okay for me to sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure. I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The butler and the maids, please take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks anyway. I feel more comfortable standing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure, I captured this suspicious man in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! This man is gardener of this house, Doi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gardener?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been like this since the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what you ask him, he stays silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was in the garden when Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was shot in the audio room at 8 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was on the surveillance camera the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the case happened, he was the only one who wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's better to see than hear 100 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to watch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The surveillance video.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was in the yard when the shots were fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, but after that you don't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it recorded the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the light kept moving,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he seems to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if only every room had a surveillance camera,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who, where and what they're doing would all be clear after watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But according to the video, we know it wasn't the doing of a stranger,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So there's a high possibility that it's an inside job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because there are so many surveillance cameras,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But not a single one recorded someone suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if you think about it, this person must be familiar with the layout of the cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only suspects left are the 4 maids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they were with all of us since the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see if they would know of any motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you're doing good today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You usually disappear on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because those two have said most of what I wanted to, so there's nothing for me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this case is very weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:37.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The butler and Motoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were with us watching the monitors when the first gunshot was fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when the second and third shots occurred, they have no alibis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you could see after the first shot was the light, and not Doi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shigeru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who doesn't have an alibi when the first shot occurred,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was with us when the second one occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If either the surveillance camera's video...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:09:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or the second and third gunshots were the trick,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of their alibis should crumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There also two doubtful points.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was there a pause for three minutes between the first and the second gunshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the book that he was reading before his death, there's a cord used as the bookmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though there was a gun supposedly aimed at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? The one who hates the master the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Among those four people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be the butler, Ueki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since master sent him to the attic which was full of dust, it has caused his asthma to act up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if I was in Shigeru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}'s position, I would be mad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since the master got the inheritance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the home Shigeru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has lived in ever since he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet he still charges him rent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's seems like Motoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} doesn't hate the master, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:54.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We all know the marriage was 'cause of the house property.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe if the master was to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who would be the happiest would be Motoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That gardener, Doi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, is always glaring at the young mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:05.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:11.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's been talking to the master about turning the garden into a swimming pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the garden which the late madame loved the most before her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough, come on back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can it be that Doi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s hometown is in Kouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lived in Takajou city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takajou city, eh?! What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'m from Kami city!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kami city?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:45.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was a child I always went swimming in the Kagami river!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really! The Kagami is really a very clear river.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even Sakamoto Ryouma went swimming there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To-Tosa accent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yukiko, you were born in Kouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! But when she was an actress...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:04.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She played a role that spoke with a Tosa accent. She learned it at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:08.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When it comes to stuff like that she's a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least that's what Shinichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r} said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, did that yield anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He said some very interesting things!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He heard the gunshot several seconds after the sound of the glass breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:31.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Usually the gunshot and the glass smashing should happen at the same time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows! Maybe he broke the glass with the gun, then shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the gunshot should sound just after the sound of breaking glass, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he doesn't remember how many gunshots he heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He thought some bad kids nearby were setting off fireworks as a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he didn't mind it much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that Yuusaku's hint has something to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Did you contact your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:11:59.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I called him just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I explained the case to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuusaku told me as he was laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Signpost for the wrong road."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted me to pass it on like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pass it on to whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, urn... Of course to Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should be grateful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:23.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't the investigation done?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:40.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We couldn't have committed this crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've spoken to the neighbors nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody has seen a suspicious character.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we haven't confirmed the gun trajectory yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the bullets which were used to kill the victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that one which was used to threaten him are from the same gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's one thing that's very strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the three bullets which were taken out of the corpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason, the lines are more shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not "eh."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your expression's tells me that you've figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter, either way, I figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So tell me, Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't be appearing on stage as the Night Baroness again, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be alright. It'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll settle it cool tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's already 11 PM!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we continue tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, we're still investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Investigating what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hasn't it been over for a while now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're all being fooled by the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seemed that Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was being threatened with a gun from outside the window, then he was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:13:59.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what a sham
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One can't fool the detective's eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:11.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This Night Baroness's private eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey hey hey, where did you get so many lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then could it be, Yukiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know who the criminal is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:22.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's all clear now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what trick did the criminal use?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be the surveillance cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were being tricked long before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal misled us with those two memos and that one bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we certainly thought he would use a gun, a signpost that led us down the wrong road.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, wasn't Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} really shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you notice it, Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the book that Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was reading before his death...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's still the cord which he used as a bookmark!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Now that you mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Usually you put the cord in at the page where you stop reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who's being threatened with a gun wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you wanted a break from reading a book, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... Turn my head, or move my shoulders...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:21.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'd stretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} just stood up and stretched.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} collapsed! Are you saying he collapsed because of stretching?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not because of stretching, but there was a problem when he stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's happened to you before, when you suddenly stand up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You begin to feel like you're going to lose consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how could he calculate the timing so precisely?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a drug that would make it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:50.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The medical name is... Isopu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isopuro... Isopu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isoproterenol.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The drug is for patients who faints or gets dizzy often.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:16:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It makes it easier for them to faint to find out why it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, he used this medicine to induce fainting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And planned for when he raised his hands and fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, at that time he wasn't shot yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the criminal didn't think that was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He completely misled us to a wrong road with those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:27.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Master has his hands raised!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were all fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:37.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Isn't that right, the butler, Ueki Shouhachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's Ueki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} then he could've put the poison in his coffee before he drank it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he also knows that he usually stretches after reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This medicine is usually used for people who have asthma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he did this to create an alibi for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He pretended to go get the key to the audio room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went around to the room from the outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And shot at the dizzy Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} three times and killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you only hear d the sound of gunshot in front of the room twice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, just now Yukiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} asked Doi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he heard the sound of the gunshot several seconds after the glass was smashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore the classical music was playing very loudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know what happened now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ri-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a silencer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He shot the first time with a silencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you only heard the sound of the glass breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And why the lines on the bullet were shallow was 'cause of the silencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the reason we didn't have a gunpowder reaction was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of the towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's find the silencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the butler still has it hidden on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's in his socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's here! The silencer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:03.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't want to take a seat, did he? So I found that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he doesn't sit down, his socks won't be exposed. He did this to cover something in his sock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wa-Wait a moment! Doesn't this burn hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:15.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can handle something of this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as I could protect the late madame's garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:23.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! This house's garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The young madame had treasured and maintained the garden since she was very young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel that the young madame is still living somewhere in this garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To leave it to that master who has nothing to do with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! So you're just the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought my enemy was this brother, Shigeru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this case, I'll get even less of the heritage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:55.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all the hard work I went through, hiring a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a big failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? About the distribution of the heritage...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has no parents or sibling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His wife will inherit all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His brother-in-lav/ shouldn't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Motoka made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's if Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't make a will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please pay 10 million yen for seeking out the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah? Why? Wasn't Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} murdered?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! I didn't promise you that I'd protect his life in the contract, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your signature and seal are both here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay! As long as I get Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s heritage...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pay you 10 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:39.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, before the inheritance is confirmed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:42.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The property under Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s name will be frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'You can only pay me with your own assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah? It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you refuse, we'll sue you and confiscate your property.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:19:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:02.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mikio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s will was read.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To those who can't protect my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't give a single yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would rather contribute it to our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:10.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how the passage was written.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the next day...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go, dear. This is 1 million, 943 thousand yen after deducting your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should thank me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Do you smell some strange scent?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's cause this morning, a client was here with her dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.82,0:22:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really Yukiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, it's been a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. I have something to ask you, Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, ask him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Yukiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} said she wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They want to know something about the Miss Teitan High School competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.08,0:22:18.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle, which one did you vote for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that one from 20 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's probably Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These two were lovey-dovey at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be Yukiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.60,0:22:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was unbelievably cute at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.81,0:22:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember, I voted for Eri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time I didn't understand it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought that 'miss' meant mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I wrote that clumsy woman's name on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So after you know the meaning of miss, who will you vote for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.12,0:22:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll vote for my very pretty, lovely Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.34,0:23:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! No! Although Eri likes reading books, she's still so popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:09.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, right, right, the payment for helping you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.14,0:23:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yukiko and I will take 10 percent, or 1 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:17.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I'll pay the debt for the bar, the snacks, and the Poirot coffee shop downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.23,0:23:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My allowance, and the cost of living for next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.11,0:23:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the laundry charge for the pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, you're change.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.86,0:23:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only 4,382 yen was left?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Yukiko, let's go eat some delicious stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.42,0:23:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So which one did win the Miss Teitan contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.47,0:23:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That car had been following our car for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.31,0:23:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.81,0:24:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought too. So I left just before the light turned red.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.48,0:24:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder who it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.07,0:24:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.03,0:24:15.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Secret of the Touto Film Developer Place. Part 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.50,0:24:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Together with Hanga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.29,0:24:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.00,0:24:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Messy room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.13,0:24:25.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad Conan! Summer vacation is almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.63,0:24:26.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Second semester has already started.
